{"tid":1949653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Dllm 有班疑似中咗招嘅支那人逾期居留","createTime":"2020-03-29T20:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T20:13:50.000Z","uid":181769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d45256ecddb2dbd4b46b6af9e535552d20718fa","tid":1949653,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:12:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200330&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60773348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200330%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60773348&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=a8ec2642\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200330%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60773348&h=74389217\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200330&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60773348</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: 蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】警查劏房揭內地人逾期居留 一屋5人疑集體發燒送院<br />\n<br />\n油麻地彌敦道525號寶寧大廈，凌晨零時許，油麻地一隊特遣隊警員，在大廈內進行反罪案巡邏期間，在一間劏房門外發現數名可疑男子聚集，警員上前截獲5人盤查，各人持有內地身份證件，但均發現逾期居留。據悉，5人來自廣東。<br />\n<br />\n警方被步調查相信，5人逾期居留期間，一直在大廈內一間劏房居住，警員替各人測量體溫，揭發5人均出現體溫偏高情況，於是通知上峰召救護員到場，3輛救護員到達現場，救護員穿上保護衣服上樓，由警員陪同協助將5人送院診治。"},{"pid":"756e6e37e545e43df209808c80047bc017203a20","tid":1949653,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516fd5735c3f5f4ec29d377b082062bb5e482108","tid":1949653,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:13:11.000Z","msg":"班狗仲摸身摸勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47ad48adb7621032314f319e0a69a247fa9d9c","tid":1949653,"uid":92979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T20:13:50.000Z